error[E0277]: this scope does not support scoped creation
  --> tests/ui/create_scoped_not_scope.rs:11:13
   |
11 |     let _ = toasty::create!(in 42_i64 { name: "Carl" });
   |             ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ this relation scope cannot create records
